---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Reveal } from '../../components/Reveal';

const title = "Chi Core Release Massage (Chi Nei Tsang) — With Miro Kloosterman";
const description = "Chi Nei Tsang — a belly and organ massage that reaches stored emotions the way nothing else does. With Miro Kloosterman.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Section 1 — Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center px-section-x pt-24 overflow-hidden grain bg-deep-forest">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img 
        src="https://picsum.photos/seed/miro-chi-nei-tsang/1920/1080" 
        alt="Chi Core Release Massage" 
        class="object-cover w-full h-full opacity-40"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full z-10">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <span class="label !text-gold">Session Modality</span>
          <h1 class="text-white mb-8">Chi Core Release Massage.</h1>
          <p class="font-body text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-sand/80 mb-8 tracking-wide">
            Also called Chi Nei Tsang. A belly and organ massage that works with stored emotion as directly as any modality I've ever trained in.
          </p>
          <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a Discovery Call</a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2 — The Work -->
  <section class="bg-sand py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <Reveal client:load>
            <h2 class="sticky top-32">What it is.</h2>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-12">
          <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg font-light text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Chi Nei Tsang is an old practice. The belly holds emotion — grief, fear, old trauma, the things the mind has moved past but the body is still carrying. A Chi Core Release session works with that directly. Gentle pressure on specific points, attentive bodywork, and the kind of holding that lets a client actually feel what they've been carrying without getting overwhelmed by it.</p>
              <p>Most sessions run around ninety minutes. Longer sessions are available when the work calls for it.</p>
            </div>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3 — What happens -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <Reveal client:load>
            <h2 class="sticky top-32">What happens.</h2>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8 text-lg font-light text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
          <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
            <p>We start slowly. I explain what I'm doing before I do it. You stay fully clothed or dressed as you're comfortable — we work through the belly, specific pressure points, and whatever the session opens up.</p>
            <p>Emotional release is common. Crying, sometimes laughter, sometimes a kind of physical lightness that's hard to describe in advance. Some clients experience memories surfacing. Some feel nothing emotional in the session and notice something shifting days later. All of that is normal. Nothing is required of you except to be there.</p>
            <p>After the bodywork, we sit. We talk about what came up if you want to, or we stay quiet. I don't rush the end of a session.</p>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4 — What it addresses -->
  <section class="bg-sand py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <Reveal client:load>
            <h2 class="sticky top-32">What it addresses.</h2>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
              <div>
                <span class="label !text-gold">Physical</span>
                <div class="space-y-4 mt-8">
                  {[
                    "Supports the detox system",
                    "Improves breathing",
                    "Reduces chronic pain",
                    "Improves lymphatic flow",
                    "Strengthens the immune system",
                    "Stimulates organ function"
                  ].map(item => (
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                      <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gold rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
                      <span class="font-body text-sm font-light text-charcoal">{item}</span>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="label !text-gold">Emotional</span>
                <div class="space-y-4 mt-8">
                  {[
                    "Balances emotions",
                    "Releases stuck grief",
                    "Increases self-awareness",
                    "Relieves deep-seated tensions",
                    "Improves sleep",
                    "Restores vitality"
                  ].map(item => (
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                      <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gold rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
                      <span class="font-body text-sm font-light text-charcoal">{item}</span>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Reveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5 — Testimonial -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <blockquote class="pull-quote">
          "During the first session I experienced the most intense crying in my whole life. It was grief of being a vanished twin. After this session I can say that my life shifted completely."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-2xl text-deep-forest mt-8">— Maria Johanna</p>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6 — Closing CTA -->
  <section class="bg-deep-forest pt-section-y pb-16 px-section-x grain relative">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <h2 class="text-white mb-8">Ready to release?</h2>
        <p class="text-sand/60 text-xl font-light mb-16 leading-relaxed">The work starts with a thirty-minute discovery call. No pitch, no script, no pressure.</p>
        <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a Discovery Call</a>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
